casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Demario Robehier WADE-BEY, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157349
COA: 335045 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 29, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for immediate consideration is GRANTED. The motion for reconsideration of this Court's April 2, 2019 order and the request for peremptory reversal are considered, and they are DENIED, because we are not persuaded that reconsideration of our previous order is warranted. MCR 7.311(G).
